<h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-bold lg: tracking-tight xl:tracking-tighter mt-4 justify-center flex pt-8">
  Available Rental Homes</h2>
  <p class="w-full pt-8 text-lg">
    Just like our RTO options, we improve on existing housing inventory with our in-house contractors to give local homeseekers more flexible options. <br/>
        See one you like? Submit an application through our tenant portal on <a href="https://southardhomesllc.app.doorloop.com/tenant-portal/rental-applications/listing?companyId=6747587dc1f13e76f53fc0f8&source=CompanyLink" target="_blank" class="text-[#ffca28] font-bold">Doorloop</a>*.</br>
